latestIgtvVideos.title: #StyleKaroDanceKaro#episode 3#formalwear #heels
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In today's fast-paced environment, as everyone around deals with the stress of meeting with deadlines and battling long work hours, many of us have heard the common phrase of maintaining a "work-life balance". 
So how do you create this work-life balance?
Inculcating the habit of taking out some time from our day-to-day routines and trying out any form of physical activity rejuvenates not only our body but also our mind and spirit. 
To me, dance is my way to express and escape from the chaos around me.

Tag your workaholic friend who needs to see this

Ps: Dancing on heels was challenging and something new which i tried for the first time🙈👠
